title: (x) "Experimente 60.30.10" script-like slab serif - Ink Gothic Alt {Yves}
content:
Hello everyone, I tried a lot of possibilities, but nothing seems to be a perfect match.

Could someone help me with this one, please?

Thanks!

comments.content:
This is [Brian J. Bonislawsky](http://web.archive.org/web/20080328212836/http:/www.typophile.com/wiki/Brian%252BJ.%252BBonislawsky) and [Brian Jaramillo](http://web.archive.org/web/20080328212836/http:/www.typophile.com/wiki/Brian%252BJaramillo)’s [Ink Gothic Alt](http://web.archive.org/web/20080328212836/http:/www.veer.com/products/typedetail.aspx?image=UMT0000131#flont).

Sorry it took me so long to get to your request, but more than 100 new requests flooded the Type Identification Board since yesterday, so I have a bit of trouble keeping up (it’s not like I haven’t got anything else to do :^P).

Thanks a lot, and don’t worry, for the price I pay you your “time response” was perfect!!!

Jorge Marcedo  
Coimbra | Portugal
